snippet.textDisplay: I hate expansions, They keep causing grief for the existing player base. My server along with others were wiped to day one. then 6 days later we get it back with a roll back of about a day. I am thankful we got most of our stuff back but we have server lag every 15 min for backups so why would our restore be over a day old? on top of that the same day I we get the server back they do another patch for Genesis that wiped my survivor and my Dino's are slowly starving to death and I'm sure my base with auto wipe before I get a response from support. Why can't they beta test the new stuff, you know how many players would hop on a beta server with a new map knowing its going to get wiped just to see it? all the free beta testers you could want! yet here we are playing an alpha game and losing all hope of keeping what we work so hard for.
